address2: Unit 1209 Shun Tak Centre 168-200 Connaught Road
longBusinessSummary: China Healthwise Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, sells Chinese health products in Hong Kong and The People's Republic of China. The company operates through three segments: Chinese Health Products, Money Lending Business, and Investment in Financial Instruments. It sells Chinese and other pharmaceutical products, health products, ginseng, and dried seafood products to wholesalers and retailers. The company also sells Chinese health products online. In addition, it provides loans; and invests in financial instruments. The company was formerly known as Haier Healthwise Holdings Limited and changed its name to China Healthwise Holdings Limited in January 2017. China Healthwise Holdings Limited is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.
